OL,3,C'Completely unacceptable': EasyJet's
OL,4,Cbank holiday warning on EU border
OL,5,Cdelays
OL,7,FThe boss of one of Europe's biggest
OL,8,Fairlines has berated the EU's new
OL,9,Fborder system, which has led to long
OL,10,Fdelays.
OL,12,FChief executive of EasyJet, Kenton
OL,13,FJarvis, told ITV News on Thursday:
OL,14,F"It's completely unacceptable, they've
OL,15,Fhad since 2017 to prepare for this
OL,16,Feventuality, and they've obviously
OL,17,Fdone a very poor job".
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@UO]
