OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779358003
OL,3,C'Completely unacceptable': EasyJet's
OL,4,Cbank holiday warning on EU border
OL,5,Cdelays
OL,7,FThis is the first peak summer period
OL,8,Fwhere the EU's controversial new entry/
OL,9,Fexit system is in operation, affecting
OL,10,Fmany of the most popular holiday
OL,11,Fdestinations for UK travellers.
OL,13,FJarvis says the EU countries 'don't
OL,14,Fneed to leave people in long queues'
OL,16,FThe system involves registering
OL,17,Ffingerprints and facial images at
OL,18,Fspecial kiosks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
