FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779358003
OL,3,C'Completely unacceptable': EasyJet's
OL,4,Cbank holiday warning on EU border
OL,5,Cdelays
OL,7,FIn April, around 100 EasyJet
OL,8,Fpassengers were left in Milan after
OL,9,Fthe new border checks delayed them.
OL,11,FThe airline's boss defended leaving
OL,12,Fpassengers behind, saying "our crews
OL,13,Fhave regulated hours where they can
OL,14,Ffly and if you wait too long the crew
OL,15,Fwill go out of hours and not be able
OL,16,Fto complete the flight, so we have no
OL,17,Fchoice".
OL,19,FThe airline is writing to EU states
OL,20,Fdemanding that they use greater
OL,21,Fflexibility to ease disruption.
OL,26,@tD@[OUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
