FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779358003
OL,3,C'Completely unacceptable': EasyJet's
OL,4,Cbank holiday warning on EU border
OL,5,Cdelays
OL,7,FJarvis urged EU member states to make
OL,8,Fuse of the flexibility available to
OL,9,Fthem to ease long border queues,
OL,10,Fsaying, 'In some airports you just
OL,11,Fsail straight through - in others the
OL,12,Fqueues can last an hour or so, and
OL,13,Fthat's not acceptable. They have
OL,14,Fflexibility, they should use it'
OL,16,FThe Easyjet chief says the new system
OL,17,Fshould be introduced at quieter times.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779358003
OL,3,C'Completely unacceptable': EasyJet's
OL,4,Cbank holiday warning on EU border
OL,5,Cdelays
OL,7,F"Do it when the airports are quiet,
OL,8,Fwhen fewer flights are coming in. If
OL,9,Fyou've got a Saturday at the start of
OL,10,Fbank holiday or half term, then
OL,11,Fobviously be sensible," he said.
OL,13,FITV News has spoken to dozens of air
OL,14,Fpassengers from a variety of airlines
OL,15,Fthat have been disrupted by the new
OL,16,Fborder checks.
OL,18,FAirline bosses say the EU should use
OL,19,Fflexibility to suspend the checks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
