OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779358003
OL,3,C'Completely unacceptable': EasyJet's
OL,4,Cbank holiday warning on EU border
OL,5,Cdelays
OL,7,FEasyJet's boss says problems are
OL,8,F"easing" since the scheme was first
OL,9,Fintroduced.
OL,11,FSome EasyJet passengers say they've
OL,12,Ffaced high prices booking replacement
OL,13,Fflights after being left behind.
OL,15,FKenton Jarvis said: "Naturally, we
OL,16,Fhave no financial obligation because
OL,17,Four obligation was to bring the
OL,18,Faircraft to the gate, wait for the
OL,19,Fpassengers and fly on the scheduled
OL,20,Ftime".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@HO]wD@UOU|D@EO]
